Pre-Game Insights: Djibouti and Ethiopia are both struggling in their World Cup qualifying campaign.
Djibouti is aiming for their first points in the qualifiers, while Ethiopia is searching for their third victory.
Djibouti has a daunting task ahead as they have lost all five meetings against Ethiopia.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match is the third for both teams in the World Cup qualifiers.
The venue is Stade Ben Ahmed El Abdi in Djibouti.
